Local Char TITSEL(30)(1..3)
Call TEXTE(3211,TITSEL(1)) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(282,TITSEL(2)) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(72,TITSEL(3)) From OBJDIV
